HEADWORD: Redcap
<hw>Red"cap`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The
European goldfinch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A specter having long teeth, popularly supposed to
haunt old castles in Scotland.</def> <mark>[Scot.]</mark>
<rj><au>Jamieson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

